WEBVTT

00:00.149 --> 00:02.409
The amazing thing about souks around the Arab world...

00:02.503 --> 00:05.448
...is they're known as places that sell everything...

00:05.627 --> 00:08.393
...from spices, to textiles, to ornaments.

00:08.637 --> 00:11.431
Anything that you can think of, you will find it here.

00:13.437 --> 00:19.986
It wouldn't truly be a gold souk in Dubai if we weren't breaking world records:...

00:20.263 --> 00:23.220
...the world's largest gold ring.

00:23.710 --> 00:24.236
This is it.

00:25.369 --> 00:29.932
Sixty-three kilograms of gold and precious stones.

00:30.133 --> 00:33.353
Sixty-three kilograms; it's almost the same weight as me.

